00:00:02.460 --> 00:00:13.020 align:middle line:90%


00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:18.210 align:middle line:84%
>>Eastern Wisdom and Modern
Life with Alan W. Watts.

00:00:18.210 --> 00:00:21.840 align:middle line:90%


00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:27.595 align:middle line:84%
Produced by KQED, San
